## Test 12 — FR-3.2: Fordringskompleks-propagation (2 medlemmer)

Ref: petition070 TC-12
GIL § 18a, stk. 2, 4. pkt.: Afbrydelse for fordring 101 i kompleks med ID 1
(fordringIds = [101, 102]) propagerer automatisk til fordring 102. Begge fordringer
får nyFristUdloeber = |2027-04-01|. propagationFuldstaendig skal være true.

```catala
declaration scope ForaeldelseTest12:
  comp scope Fordringskompleks

scope ForaeldelseTest12:
  # Test: FR-3.2 — fordringskompleks-propagation → begge medlemmer får ny frist
  # Ref: petition070 TC-12 / ForaeldelseTest12
  # antalMedlemmer = 2 (kompleks-struct: stamfordring 101 + rentekrav 102)
  definition comp.antalMedlemmer equals 2
  definition comp.harAfbrydelse equals true
  definition comp.sharedNyFrist equals |2027-04-01|
  assertion comp.propagationFuldstaendig = true
  assertion comp.kompleksNyFristUdloeber = |2027-04-01|
```

---

## Test 13 — FR-4.3: Tillægsfrist max() branch A (currentFristExpires > eventDate)

Ref: petition070 TC-13
G.A.2.4.4.2: Tillægsfrist = max(currentFristExpires, eventDate) + 2 år.
Branch A: currentFristExpires = |2026-01-01| > eventDate = |2025-03-15|.
max(|2026-01-01|, |2025-03-15|) = |2026-01-01|; + 2 år = |2028-01-01|.
Denne branch beviser at en eksisterende frist der udløber senere end
eventDate + 2 år IKKE forkortes.

```catala
declaration scope ForaeldelseTest13:
  comp scope TillaegsfristBeregning

scope ForaeldelseTest13:
  # Test: FR-4.3 branch A — currentFristExpires > eventDate → nyFristUdloeber = |2028-01-01|
  # Ref: petition070 TC-13 / ForaeldelseTest13
  definition comp.currentFristExpires equals |2026-01-01|
  definition comp.eventDate equals |2025-03-15|
  definition comp.udskydelseDato equals |2021-11-20|
  definition comp.erTomt equals false
  assertion comp.nyFristUdloeber = |2028-01-01|
```

---

## Test 14 — FR-4.3: Tillægsfrist max() branch B (eventDate > currentFristExpires)

Ref: petition070 TC-14
G.A.2.4.4.2: Tillægsfrist = max(currentFristExpires, eventDate) + 2 år.
Branch B: eventDate = |2025-09-30| > currentFristExpires = |2025-01-01|.
max(|2025-01-01|, |2025-09-30|) = |2025-09-30|; + 2 år = |2027-09-30|.
Begge branches (T-13 og T-14) tilsammen beviser at max()-formlen er nødvendig.

```catala
declaration scope ForaeldelseTest14:
  comp scope TillaegsfristBeregning

scope ForaeldelseTest14:
  # Test: FR-4.3 branch B — eventDate > currentFristExpires → nyFristUdloeber = |2027-09-30|
  # Ref: petition070 TC-14 / ForaeldelseTest14
  definition comp.currentFristExpires equals |2025-01-01|
  definition comp.eventDate equals |2025-09-30|
  definition comp.udskydelseDato equals |2021-11-20|
  definition comp.erTomt equals false
  assertion comp.nyFristUdloeber = |2027-09-30|
```

---

## Test 15 — FR-4.2: Foreløbig afbrydelse for tomt fordringskompleks (GIL § 18a, stk. 7)

Ref: petition070 TC-15
GIL § 18a, stk. 7: Når fordringskomplekset er tomt (erTomt = true) medfører en
afbrydelseshændelse en foreløbig afbrydelse (FORELOEBIG_AFBRYDELSE) med 3-årig frist
fra eventDate. Med eventDate |2024-07-01| er nyFristUdloeber = |2027-07-01|.

```catala
declaration scope ForaeldelseTest15:
  comp scope TillaegsfristBeregning

scope ForaeldelseTest15:
  # Test: FR-4.2 — erTomt = true → FORELOEBIG_AFBRYDELSE, nyFristUdloeber = |2027-07-01|
  # Ref: petition070 TC-15 / ForaeldelseTest15
  definition comp.erTomt equals true
  definition comp.eventDate equals |2024-07-01|
  definition comp.currentFristExpires equals |2025-01-01|
  definition comp.udskydelseDato equals |2021-11-20|
  assertion comp.afbrydelseResultat = FORELOEBIG_AFBRYDELSE
  assertion comp.nyFristUdloeber = |2027-07-01|
```

